          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4465736372697074696f6e23232344415441232323">Models equipped with Jump Packs are Jump Infantry. Space Marines wearing jump packs can be kept in reserve and arrive using the Deep Strike rules, but only if the mission allows for Deep Strike to be used.</characteristic>
