      </costs>
      <rules>
        <rule name="Blessing of the Omnissiah" id="6aa5-6ff5-7a87-b0af" hidden="false">
          <description>The model may repair Immobilized or Weapon Destroyed results instead of moving. A Techmarine (or Tech-Adept) must be in contact with a vehicle. Roll a D6. A6 is required to make the repair. Add +1 to the roll for each servitor equipped with a servo arm in the Techmarine&apos;s unit. You may reroll the die if the Techmarine is equipped with a servo-harness.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
      <comment>Blood Angels 4E</comment>
    </selectionEntry>
